      <h3 style="color:#1a325d; font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700;">What’s draining your energy:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Aggressive or confrontational tones.</li>
        <li>Unclear expectations and last-minute changes.</li>
        <li>Feeling isolated or left out of decisions.</li>
